  "original_title": "50 \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One arrested with 50 tear gas shells",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Police Media Unit has informed that a person has been arrested in connection with the incident of attacking a group of police officers and stealing 50 teargas shells from them during a demonstration near Poltua Junction, Pattaramullai on 13th July.",
        "Commenting on the incident, Police Media Spokesperson, Senior Superintendent of Police Nihal Talduwa said,",
        "During the anti-government demonstration near Poltua Junction, a police team carrying 50 tear gas shells on a three-wheeler blocked the three-wheeler and attacked the police officers and 50 tear gas shells were stolen from them by the protesters.",
        "In this case, the suspect in connection with the said incident, Obeysekara, has been arrested by the Welikadai police in Pura Nanayakkara Mavathi.",
        "Also, Poralai is a temporary resident of Gotami area and has hidden 50 tear gas shells in his dormitory room.",
        "He further informed that the arrested person is a 31-year-old from Polonnaruwa area and the suspect will be produced in the Magistrate's Court."
      ],
